          Call    SetMessageValue ( *Var8 00000002 ) % bp cost
          Call    SpeakToPlayer ( .Npc:Self 00A70004 00A70001 00000000 00270017 ) % Confirmation
          Call    ShowChoice ( 001E000D ) % Yes No
